<div><h3>MPA 3170 - Change Management </h3>  <hr>Focuses on how to empower staff to embrace and operationalize a new corporate vision and to understand the new strategic intent when organizations undergo rapid transformations. Students explore ways for managers to develop a new vision for the organization and/or bring the base of the organization into line with strategic change in light of mergers, acquisitions, privatization, and/or shifts in product or product lines.<br><br><strong>Anticipated Terms Offered:</strong> varies<br><br></div>		</td>
